{"tid":1008970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"濕疹少女做義工 學會「放低」重拾自信","createTime":"2019-02-05T00:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T17:07:08.000Z","uid":18739,"like":76,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"bea6f7ffa64012b598706c3ef164ae5dab2fa4b9","tid":1008970,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T00:01:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20190204/s00002/1549216388677/濕疹少女做義工-學會「放低」重拾自信\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190204%2Fs00002%2F1549216388677%2F%E6%BF%95%E7%96%B9%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%81%9A%E7%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5-%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%83%E3%80%8C%E6%94%BE%E4%BD%8E%E3%80%8D%E9%87%8D%E6%8B%BE%E8%87%AA%E4%BF%A1&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ4oeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=9c59c3e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190204%2Fs00002%2F1549216388677%2F%E6%BF%95%E7%96%B9%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%81%9A%E7%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5-%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%83%E3%80%8C%E6%94%BE%E4%BD%8E%E3%80%8D%E9%87%8D%E6%8B%BE%E8%87%AA%E4%BF%A1&h=fc9905fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20190204/s00002/1549216388677/濕疹少女做義工-學會「放低」重拾自信</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Phs4E2Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPhs4E2Z.png&h=2c0dde4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NzYoa9F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNzYoa9F.png&h=1311d4db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】劉羨文（Sammi）初中時不愛說話，更沒自信，因她患有濕疹，皮膚「全部都紅了」，加上學習壓力，常有負面情緒。但她開始做義工後重拾自己價值，學會坦然面對困難，就如接受「我的皮膚就是這樣」。<br />\n<br />\n18歲的Sammi現為大學一年級生，已做義工近5年。她自小患濕疹，初中時更嚴重，頸、頭、身「全部都紅了，會不斷甩皮」。Sammi當時很在意外貌，夏天會想「遮遮掩掩」，不希望接觸旁人。現時回想，她感激中三當年自己願意踏出做義工的一步。<br />\n<br />\nSammi中三時，老師提議她當義工幫助流浪貓狗，她後來更任校內義工隊主席，感染同學做義工，慢慢地「找到自己價值，愈來愈有自信心、懂與他人相處」。Sammi分享，一次與一名智障孩童的母親傾談，該母親因孩子的狀况，與丈夫婚姻亦出問題，生活變艱難，更一度有輕生念頭，但後來接受孩子與他人不同的事實。Sammi說，做義工時會放下負面情緒，那次傾談令她覺得要「放得低」，坦然面對生活困難，讓自己更快樂。<br />\n<br />\n中六堅持做義工 父母見女兒開心變支持<br />\n<br />\nSammi高中時學業繁重，仍堅持做義工，有時年初一亦因而沒拜年，父母曾反對她花過多時間做義工，後來見她變得開心，轉為支持，甚至一同做義工。Sammi說中六時濕疹好轉，除了定時吃藥，覺得做義工令心情開朗亦有影響。她希望日後參與更多各類義工活動，亦覺得可推廣更多長者當義工。<br />\n<br />\n社署2000年起推出「香港傑出青年義工計劃」，每年選約20名16至24歲義工，提供培訓及交流團，Sammi是2018至19年度其中一名獲選者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家係靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重拾信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec80a11aaae525d61fd494aadc29bad90bab0dd","tid":1008970,"uid":78429,"like":87,"dislike":0,"score":87,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T00:09:52.000Z","msg":"靚嘅走出嚟搞啲咁嘅嘢只會造就更多冇自信嘅人"},{"pid":"33416db0b5fdd38fe51dfabd823ed4b9a607a64c","tid":1008970,"uid":3302,"like":32,"dislike":17,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T00:11:19.000Z","msg":"好正<br />\n好撚想搞大條衰妹個肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c9048ce556a239af160f37ef845ff79bd7ae49","tid":1008970,"uid":25345,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T00:35:08.000Z","msg":"即係佢見到人地更慘,所以自己幸福d?<br />\n睇人仆街最開心?"},{"pid":"352ae963f01be6169462a9c4fc35ac800a8f525d","tid":1008970,"uid":146435,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"49c9048ce556a239af160f37ef845ff79bd7ae49","tid":1008970,"uid":25345,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T00:35:08.000Z","msg":"即係佢見到人地更慘,所以自己幸福d?<br />\n睇人仆街最開心?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05